  "description": "Input 48V 802.3af Output 24V 0.5A PoE Gigabit Adapter",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Outdoor PoE Conversion for Non-PoE Devices",
      "text": "The Instant Outdoor PoE (Power over Ethernet) Converter from Ubiquiti, designated by the manufacture part number INS-3AF-O-G, is a robust device engineered to adapt non-PoE compliant Ubiquiti equipment to operate with PoE-enabled networks in outdoor settings. This capability simplifies the deployment of outdoor network equipment by eliminating the need for separate power sources, reducing installation complexity, and enhancing system reliability. Compatible with airMAX® and UniFi® devices and offer an easy Plug and Play setup. It operates transparently, allowing for immediate deployment without technical complications."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Longer Cable Runs",
      "text": "High voltage carries power more efficiently. The Instant 802.3af Gigabit PoE Converter enables longer cable runs due to a more efficient power delivery."
    },
    {
      "heading": "ESD/Surge Protection",
      "text": "Instant 802.3af Converters provide an additional ±15kV of Ethernet isolation to lessen the risk of ESD or surge damage to connected devices."
    },
    {
      "heading": "PoE Switch Compatibility",
      "text": "The Instant 802.3af Gigabit PoE Converter integrates seamlessly with a variety of auto-sensing 802.3af PoE switches for remote power control applications. As you manage and monitor your network, you can conveniently power or power cycle your remote devices using your 802.3af switch."
    }
  ],
